00:00:46.690 --> 00:00:53.130
When I take off the lock screen, you can see a writing program that is run immediately.

00:00:53.140 --> 00:00:59.540
The sensing method to pull out pen like this is by using a sensor that detects magnetic properties.

00:00:59.550 --> 00:01:03.860
There is a sensor that detects magnetic properties in the back.

00:01:03.870 --> 00:01:06.970
The back side of pen embedded the magnet.

00:01:06.980 --> 00:01:12.810
The USB port is iron. I use this USB port and try to make sure that pen back side is magnet.

00:01:12.820 --> 00:01:19.160
