00:01:19.170 --> 00:01:23.520
We can confirm the pen back side is magnet by this method.

00:01:23.530 --> 00:01:27.540
Turned on by magnets, so caution is required.

00:01:27.550 --> 00:01:37.310
When notebook is in sleep mode, accidentally if there is/are the magnet at a pen holder, the duo turns on unwanted things can happen.

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:44.350
If you don't want this function, you can disable at VAIO control center.

